INSERT INTO `assessment2` VALUES (3969,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784390808','Learning BeagleBone Python Programming','','Packt Publishing','20150714','eng','Alexander Hiam','','','<p>If you have experience with the Python language and are interested in getting started with electronics, then BeagleBone Black is the perfect platform for you and this book will provide you with the information you need.</p>','9781784399702.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3969/learning-beaglebone-python-programming'),(3970,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785289934','Learning Object-Oriented Programming','','Packt Publishing','20150716','eng','Gaston C. Hillar','','','<p>If you\'re a Python, JavaScript, or C# developer and want to learn the basics of object-oriented programming with real-world examples, then this book is for you.</p>','9781785289637.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3970/learning-objectoriented-programming'),(3971,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783552405','NGINX High Performance','','Packt Publishing','20150716','eng','Rahul Sharma','','','<p>System administrators, developers, and engineers looking for ways to achieve maximum performance from NGINX will find this book beneficial. If you are looking for solutions such as how to handle more users from the same system or load your website pages faster, then this is the book for you.</p>','9781785281839.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3971/nginx-high-performance'),(3972,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783983995','Building Web Applications with Python and Neo4j','','Packt Publishing','20150716','eng','Sumit Gupta','','','<p>If you are a Python developer and want to expand your understanding of Python-based web applications over Neo4j graph data models, this is the book for you.</p>','9781783983988.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3972/building-web-applications-with-python-and-neo4j'),(3973,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783986835','Gradle for Android','','Packt Publishing','20150717','eng','Kevin Pelgrims','','','<p>If you are an experienced Android developer wanting to enhance your skills with the Gradle Android build system, then this book is for you. As a prerequisite, you will need some knowledge of the concepts of Android application development.</p>','9781783986828.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3973/gradle-for-android'),(3974,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783553327','Mastering Julia','','Packt Publishing','20150722','eng','Malcolm Sherrington','','','<p>This hands-on guide is aimed at practitioners of data science. The book assumes some previous skills with Julia and skills in coding in a scripting language such as Python or R, or a compiled language such as C or Java.</p>','9781783553310.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3974/mastering-julia'),(3975,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783987078','Spark Cookbook','','Packt Publishing','20150727','eng','Rishi Yadav','','','<p>If you are a data engineer, an application developer, or a data scientist who would like to leverage the power of Apache Spark to get better insights from big data, then this is the book for you.</p>','9781783987061.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3975/spark-cookbook'),(3976,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785280672','Nginx Essentials','','Packt Publishing','20150722','eng','Valery Kholodkov','','','<p>This book is ideal for skilled web masters and site reliability engineers who want to switch to Nginx or solidify their knowledge of Nginx. Knowledge of Unix and webmaster skills are required.</p>','9781785289538.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3976/nginx-essentials'),(3977,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783981410','Deploying Node.js','','Packt Publishing','20150723','eng','Sandro Pasquali','','','<p>If you are an intermediate or advanced developer deploying your Node.js applications, then this book is for you. If you have already built a Node application or module and want to take your knowledge to the next level, this book will help you find your way.</p>','9781783981403.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3977/deploying-nodejs'),(3978,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785284472','Game Development with Swift','','Packt Publishing','20150723','eng','Stephen Haney','','','<p>If you wish to create and publish fun iOS games using Swift, then this book is for you. You should be familiar with basic programming concepts. However, no prior game development or Apple ecosystem experience is required.</p>','9781783550531.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3978/game-development-with-swift'),(3979,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784396046','WildFly Cookbook','','Packt Publishing','20150724','eng','Luigi Fugaro','','','<p>This book is intended for middleware system administrators and Java developers, actually good Java developers, who care about architecture design and implementation. Whether you are new to WildFly, come from a previous version, such as JBoss AS 5, 6, and 7, or are an expert in it, you will be able to master both the basic and advanced features of WildFly.</p>\r\n<p>By the way, most of the core components of WildFly are totally new, such as its administration tool, that is, the CLI; its operational modes, which are, the standalone and domain modes; and its web server provided by Undertow, you can benefit from this book even if you have no experience in JBoss and WildFly at all.</p>','9781784392413.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3979/wildfly-cookbook'),(3980,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785284373','FreeSWITCH 1.6 Cookbook','','Packt Publishing','20150722','eng','Anthony Minessale II','Michael S Collins','Giovanni Maruzzelli','<p>FreeSWITCH 1.6 Cookbook is written for anyone who wants to learn more about using FreeSWITCH in production. The information is presented in such a way that you can get up and running quickly. The cookbook approach eschews much of the foundational concepts, and instead focuses on discrete examples that illustrate specific features. If you need to implement a particular feature as quickly as possible, then this book is for you.</p>','9781785280917.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3980/freeswitch-16-cookbook'),(3981,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784393182','Moodle Administration Essentials','','Packt Publishing','20150723','eng','Gavin Henrick','Karen Holland','','<p>If you are an experienced system administrator and know how to manage servers and set up web environments but now want to explore Moodle, this book is perfect for you. You\'ll get to grips with the basics and learn to manage Moodle quickly, focusing on essential tasks. Having prior knowledge of virtual learning environments would be beneficial, but is not mandatory to make the most of this book.</p>','9781784395476.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3981/moodle-administration-essentials'),(3982,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781849515511','Lua Game Development Cookbook','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Mario Kasuba','','','<p>This book is for all programmers and game enthusiasts who want to stop dreaming about creating a game, and actually create one from scratch.\r\nThe reader should know the basics of programming and using the Lua language. Knowledge of the C/C++ programming language is not necessary, but it\'s strongly recommended in order to write custom Lua modules extending game engine capabilities or to rewrite parts of the Lua code into a more efficient form.</p>\r\n<p>Algebra and matrix operations are required in order to understand advanced topics in Chapter 4, Graphics – Legacy Method with OpenGL 1.x-2.1 and Chapter 5, Graphics – Modern Method with OpenGL 3.0+.</p>\r\n<p>Sample demonstrations are coupled with binary libraries for Windows and Linux operating systems for convenience.</p>','9781849515504.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3982/lua-game-development-cookbook'),(3983,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784392116','Arduino Electronics Blueprints','','Packt Publishing','20150724','eng','Don Wilcher','','','<p>This book is intended for those who want to learn about electronics and coding by building amazing devices and gadgets with Arduino. If you are an experienced developer who understands the basics of electronics, then you can quickly learn how to build smart devices using Arduino. The only experience needed is a desire to learn about electronics, circuit breadboarding, and coding.</p>','9781784393601.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3983/arduino-electronics-blueprints'),(3984,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783984930','Elasticsearch Blueprints','','Packt Publishing','20150724','eng','Vineeth Mohan','','','<p>If you are a data enthusiast and would like to explore and specialize on search technologies based on Elasticsearch, this is the right book for you. A compelling case-to-case mapping of features and implementation of Elasticsearch to solve many real-world use cases makes this book the right choice to start and specialize on Elasticsearch.</p>','9781783984923.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3984/elasticsearch-blueprints'),(3985,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783985517','Mastering JavaScript Promises','','Packt Publishing','20150724','eng','Muzzamil Hussain','','','<p>This book is for all the software and web engineers wanting to apply the promises paradigm to their next project and get the best outcome from it. This book also acts as a reference for the engineers who are already using promises in their projects and want to improve their current knowledge to reach the next level. To get the most benefit from this book, you should know basic programming concepts, have a familiarity with JavaScript, and a good understanding of HTML.</p>','9781783985500.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3985/mastering-javascript-promises'),(3986,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784397425','Salt Cookbook','','Packt Publishing','20150727','eng','Anirban Saha','','','<p>If you are a professional associated with system and infrastructure management, looking at automated infrastructure and deployments, then this book is for you. No prior experience of Salt is required.</p>','9781784399740.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3986/salt-cookbook'),(3987,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783552351','Android 5 Programming by Example','','Packt Publishing','20150727','eng','Kyle Mew','','','<p>If you have a great idea for a mobile app, and some familiarity with Java, or a similar procedural programming language, then all you need is this book to turn your idea into a reality.</p>','9781785288449.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3987/android-5-programming-by-example'),(3988,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785285097','Blueprints Visual Scripting for Unreal Engine','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Brenden Sewell','','','<p>Whether you are an experienced game designer or artist looking to test your latest idea, or a complete novice looking to build their first video game, this is a great place to start learning how to build complex game mechanics quickly and easily without writing any text code. No programming experience required!</p>','9781785286018.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3988/blueprints-visual-scripting-for-unreal-engine'),(3989,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784394851','Learning Laravel\'s Eloquent','','Packt Publishing','20150727','eng','Francesco Malatesta','','','<p>This book is perfect for developers with some basic knowledge of PHP development, but are new to the Eloquent ORM. However, developers with previous Laravel and Eloquent experience will also benefit from the in-depth analysis of specific classes and methodologies in the book.</p>','9781784391584.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3989/learning-laravels-eloquent'),(3990,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783980772','Oracle GoldenGate 12c Implementer\'s Guide','','Packt Publishing','20150727','eng','John P Jeffries','','','<p>The book is aimed at Oracle database administrators, project managers, and solution architects who wish to extend their knowledge of GoldenGate. The reader is assumed to be familiar with Oracle databases. No knowledge of GoldenGate is required.</p>','9781785280474.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3990/oracle-goldengate-12c-implementers-guide'),(3991,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784398507','NLTK Essentials','','Packt Publishing','20150727','eng','Nitin Hardeniya','','','<p>If you are an NLP or machine learning enthusiast with some or no experience in text processing, then this book is for you. This book is also ideal for expert Python programmers who want to learn NLTK quickly.</p>','9781784396909.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3991/nltk-essentials'),(3992,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783553488','Jenkins Essentials','','Packt Publishing','20150727','eng','Mitesh Soni','','','<p>If you are a Jenkins novice or beginner with a basic understanding of continuous integration, then this is the book for you. Beginners in Jenkins will get quick hands-on experience and gain the confidence to go ahead and explore the use of Jenkins further.</p>','9781783553471.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3992/jenkins-essentials'),(3993,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783289059','Hadoop Backup and Recovery Solutions','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Gaurav Barot','Chintan Mehta','Amij Patel','<p>If you are a Hadoop administrator and you want to get a good grounding in how to back up large amounts of data and manage Hadoop clusters, then this book is for you.</p>','9781783289042.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3993/hadoop-backup-and-recovery-solutions'),(3994,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784399306','Implementing Splunk - Second Edition','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Vincent Bumgarner','James D. Miller','','<p>If you are a data analyst with basic knowledge of Big Data analysis but no knowledge of Splunk, then this book will help you get started with Splunk. The book assumes that you have access to a copy of Splunk, ideally not in production, and many examples also assume you have administrator rights.</p>','9781784391607.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3994/implementing-splunk-second-edition'),(3995,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785281112','Learning Ionic','','Packt Publishing','20150724','eng','Arvind Ravulavaru','','','<p>This book is intended for those who want to learn how to build hybrid mobile applications using Ionic. It is also ideal for people who want to explore theming for Ionic apps. Prior knowledge of AngularJS is essential to complete this book successfully.</p>','9781783552603.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3995/learning-ionic'),(3996,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781782170990','OpenStack Cloud Security','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Fabio Alessandro Locati','','','<p>If you are an OpenStack administrator or developer, or wish to build solutions to protect your OpenStack environment, then this book is for you. Experience of Linux administration and familiarity with different OpenStack components is assumed.</p>','9781782170983.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3996/openstack-cloud-security'),(3997,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784393045','PhoneGap: Beginner\'s Guide - Third Edition','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Purusothaman Ramanujam','Giorgio Natili','','<p>This book is for web developers who want to be productive in the mobile market quickly. In fact, by using PhoneGap, it\'s possible to deploy native applications based on web standards. This book assumes a very small knowledge of HTML/CSS/JavaScript and mobile platforms, such as Android, BlackBerry, iOS, and Windows Phone, and takes the reader step-by-step into a deep overview of PhoneGap and its APIs.</p>','9781784392284.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3997/phonegap-beginners-guide-third-edition'),(3998,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783985272','Cocos2d-x Game Development Blueprints','','Packt Publishing','20150727','eng','Karan Sequeira','','','<p>If you are a proficient Cocos2d game developer who wants to enhance his or her game development skill set using Cocos2d-x to build different types of games, this book is for you.</p>','9781783985265.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3998/cocos2dx-game-development-blueprints'),(3999,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785287534','Test-Driven Development with Django','','Packt Publishing','20150730','eng','Kevin Harvey','','','<p>This book is for Django developers with little or no knowledge of test-driven development or testing in general. Familiarity with the command line, setting up a Python virtual environment, and starting a Django project are assumed.</p>','9781785281167.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/3999/testdriven-development-with-django'),(4000,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784391201','Learning Data Mining with Python','','Packt Publishing','20150729','eng','Robert Layton','','','<p>If you are a programmer who wants to get started with data mining, then this book is for you.</p>','9781784396053.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4000/learning-data-mining-with-python'),(4001,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785281259','Programming ArcGIS with Python Cookbook - Second Edition','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Eric Pimpler','','','<p>Programming ArcGIS with Python Cookbook, Second Edition, is written for GIS professionals who wish to revolutionize their ArcGIS workflow with Python. Whether you are new to ArcGIS or a seasoned professional, you almost certainly spend time each day performing various geoprocessing tasks. This book will teach you how to use the Python programming language to automate these geoprocessing tasks and make you a more efficient and effective GIS professional.</p>','9781785282898.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4001/programming-arcgis-with-python-cookbook-second-edition'),(4002,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783988211','Mastering OpenCV Android Application Programming','','Packt Publishing','20150729','eng','Salil Kapur','Nisarg Thakkar','','<p>If you are a Java and Android developer looking to enhance your skills by learning the latest features of OpenCV Android application programming, then this book is for you.</p>','9781783988204.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4002/mastering-opencv-android-application-programming'),(4003,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781849693899','Blend for Visual Studio 2012 by Example: Beginner\'s Guide','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Abhishek Shukla','','','<p>This book is aimed at developers and designers who are new to Blend and looking to learn Blend, not just practically, but also conceptually. This book does not assume any knowledge about Blend on the part of developers; however, some experience in design or development might be useful in understanding the concepts faster, but this book explains everything very simply so that you are able to understand everything with little or no effort.</p>','9781849693882.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4003/blend-for-visual-studio-2012-by-example-beginners-guide'),(4004,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783558636','Mastering Prezi for Business Presentations - Second Edition','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Russell Anderson-Williams','J.J. Sylvia IV','','<p>If you use Prezi in business and want to take your presentations to the next level, or if you want to become the office Prezi master, this book is for you.</p>','9781782175094.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4004/mastering-prezi-for-business-presentations-second-edition'),(4005,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784397302','Neo4j Graph Data Modeling','','Packt Publishing','20150727','eng','Mahesh Lal','','','<p>If you are a developer who wants to understand the fundamentals of modeling data in Neo4j and how it can be used to model full-fledged applications, then this book is for you. Some understanding of domain modeling may be advantageous but is not essential.</p>','9781784393441.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4005/neo4j-graph-data-modeling'),(4006,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783988549','PostgreSQL Replication - Second Edition','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Hans-Jurgen Schonig','','','<p>This book is ideal for PostgreSQL administrators who want to set up and understand replication. By the end of the book, you will be able to make your databases more robust and secure by getting to grips with PostgreSQL replication.</p>','9781783550609.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4006/postgresql-replication-second-edition'),(4007,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781782174912','Internet of Things with Intel Galileo','','Packt Publishing','20150729','eng','Miguel de Sousa','','','<p>This book employs an incremental, step-by-step approach to get you familiarized with everything from the basic terms, board components, and development environments to developing real projects. Each project will demonstrate how to use specific board components and tools. Both Galileo and Galileo Gen 2 are covered in this book.</p>','9781782174585.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4007/internet-of-things-with-intel-galileo'),(4008,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785284816','Kali Linux Wireless Penetration Testing Essentials','','Packt Publishing','20150730','eng','Marco Alamanni','','','<p>This book is targeted at information security professionals, penetration testers and network/system administrators who want to get started with wireless penetration testing. No prior experience with Kali Linux and wireless penetration testing is required, but familiarity with Linux and basic networking concepts is recommended.</p>','9781785280856.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4008/kali-linux-wireless-penetration-testing-essentials'),(4009,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781782174738','Sass Essentials','','Packt Publishing','20150728','eng','Alex Libby','','','<p>This book is primarily aimed at web designers who have a good understanding of CSS, jQuery, and HTML, but who are new to using CSS preprocessing. Some prior knowledge is assumed of WordPress, CSS grids, and Bootstrap, although these skills can be picked up reasonably quickly.<p/>','9781782174301.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4009/sass-essentials'),(4010,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784399511','Wireshark Network Security','','Packt Publishing','20150729','eng','Piyush Verma','','','<p>If you are network administrator or a security analyst with an interest in using Wireshark for security analysis, then this is the book for you. Basic familiarity with common network and application services terms and technologies is assumed.</p>','9781784393335.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4010/wireshark-network-security'),(4011,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783554058','Getting Started with Hazelcast - Second Edition','','Packt Publishing','20150730','eng','Mat Johns','','','<p>This book is a great introduction for Java developers, software architects, or DevOps looking to enable scalable and agile data within their applications. Providing in-memory object storage, cluster-wide state and messaging, or even scalable task execution, Hazelcast helps solve a number of issues that have troubled technologists for years.</p>','9781785285332.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4011/getting-started-with-hazelcast-second-edition'),(4012,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785281181','Microsoft Exchange Server PowerShell Cookbook - Third Edition','','Packt Publishing','20150729','eng','Jonas Andersson','Mike Pfeiffer','','<p>This book is for messaging professionals who want to build real-world scripts with Windows PowerShell 5 and the Exchange Management Shell. If you are a network or systems administrator responsible for managing and maintaining Exchange Server 2013, you will find this highly useful.</p>','9781785288074.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4012/microsoft-exchange-server-powershell-cookbook-third-edition'),(4013,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784391553','Programming Microsoft Dynamics™ NAV 2015','','Packt Publishing','20150730','eng','David Studebaker','Christopher Studebaker','','<p>This book is targeted at those who want to learn NAV\'s powerful and extensive built-in development capabilities. It assumes that you understand programming and are familiar with business application software.</p>','9781784394202.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4013/programming-microsoft-dynamics-nav-2015'),(4014,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783552740','Practical Web Development','','Packt Publishing','20150730','eng','Paul Wellens','','','<p>This book is perfect for beginners who want to get started and learn the web development basics, but also offers experienced developers a web development roadmap that will help them to extend their capabilities.</p>','9781782175919.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4014/practical-web-development'),(4015,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783984893','Blender 3D Cookbook','','Packt Publishing','20150730','eng','Enrico Valenza','','','<p>This book is aimed at the professionals that already have good 3D CGI experience with commercial packages and have now decided to try the open source Blender and want to experiment with something more complex than the average tutorials on the web.</p>\r\n<p>However, it\'s also aimed at the intermediate Blender users who simply want to go some steps further.</p>\r\n<p>It\'s taken for granted that you already know how to move inside the Blender interface, that you already have 3D modeling knowledge, and also that of basic 3D modeling and rendering concepts, for example, edge-loops, n-gons, or samples.</p>\r\n<p>In any case, it\'s also possible for a keen beginner to follow this book, by combining it with the manual on the BlenderWiki or preceding it with a basic Blender UI tutorial on the web.</p>\r\n<p>The keyboard/mouse shortcuts for the operations in the recipes are, at least in all the more relevant cases, indicated in brackets.</p>','9781783984886.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4015/blender-3d-cookbook'),(4016,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781785281297','Android Wearable Programming','','Packt Publishing','20150730','eng','Steven F. Daniel','','','<p>If you are an Android developer who wants to learn how to build applications for the Android Wear platform, then this is the book for you. This book only requires a basic knowledge of Android programming. Familiarity with development IDEs such as Android Studio, IntelliJ IDEA, or Eclipse will be helpful.</p>','9781785280153.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4016/android-wearable-programming'),(4017,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781784397210','Mastering OpenStack','','Packt Publishing','20150730','eng','Omar Khedher','','','<p>This book is intended for system administrators, cloud engineers, and system architects who want to deploy a cloud based on OpenStack in a mid- to large-sized IT infrastructure. If you have a fundamental understanding of cloud computing and OpenStack and want to expand your knowledge, then this book is an excellent checkpoint to move forward.</p>','9781784395643.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4017/mastering-openstack'),(4018,'books/RM_Books/packtpub/','9781783559091','Mastering jQuery Mobile','','Packt Publishing','20150730','eng','Chip Lambert','Shreerang Patwardhan','','<p>You\'ve started down the path of jQuery Mobile, now begin mastering some of jQuery Mobile\'s higher level topics. Go beyond jQuery Mobile\'s documentation and master one of the hottest mobile technologies out there. Previous JavaScript and PHP experience can help you get the most out of this book.</p>','9781783559084.jpg','https://www.perlego.com/book/4018/mastering-jquery-mobile');
